reviewText: Love show, but never does anything's on Tigers!
Excellent programming,a learning film,and well done. I enjoy any of Jack Hanna production because he is a real live person and not some computer derived entity.
I would rather see a lot less about Jack and more about the animals. And I'm from Columbus!
GOOD SHOW. GOOD HOME SCHOOL TOOL. FROM RGB IN TN.

I started watching these shows on Saturday mornings when cartoons were no longer of interest and really came to like them. I get to see exotic animals and exotic places. And Jack can be humorous at times. I give it a thumbs up.
